      "step_id": 0,
      "title": "Before You Begin",
      "instruction": "In preparation for the astrocyte and neuron differentiations, hiPSCs must be transduced with the TetOn-NGN2 and rTTA viruses to allow for conditional activation of the transcription factor NGN2. This section of the protocol was based on previously published work (Zhang et al., 2013). Although, other neuronal subclasses could be used in this protocol.",
